{"word":"διερῶ","slug":"διερῶ","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>διερῶ</b></el> <el>(perf <el>διείρηκα</el>) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:διερῶ'><el>διερῶ</el></a> serving as <a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a>, <el>διείρηκα</el> as <a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a>, of <a href='S:διαγορεύω'><el>διαγορεύω</el></a>\n<br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:confer, compare'>cf.</a> <a href='S:διεῖπον'><el>διεῖπον</el></a>\n<p/><i>to say fully, distinctly, expressly</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, aor1 <el>διερρήθην</el>, <a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a> <el>διείρημαι</el>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/>"}]}